issue.title: Place language in URL
issue.body:
It would be nice if the language name would be encoded in the URL. Such as:
https://site/?lang=lua

issue.title: Scalability
issue.body:
I should allow this to be more flexible and allow it to be deployed across multiple machines.

To do this:
* Avoid centralized stores - use scalable databases
* Add kube/other scheduler integration
